#. <section class="sutta" id="sn14.32"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn14.32:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 14"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 14"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn14.32:0.2"
msgid "4. Catutthavagga"
msgstr "4. The Fourth Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 32. Acariṃsutta → assādapariyesanasuttaṃ (bj) | acariṃ (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn14.32:0.3"
msgid "32. Acariṃsutta"
msgstr "32. In Search of Gratification"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn14.32:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn14.32:1.2"
msgid ""
"“Pathavīdhātuyāhaṃ, bhikkhave, assādapariyesanaṃ acariṃ, yo pathavīdhātuyā "
"assādo tadajjhagamaṃ, yāvatā pathavīdhātuyā assādo paññāya me so sudiṭṭho."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I went in search of the earth element’s gratification, and I "
"found it. I’ve seen clearly with wisdom the full extent of gratification in "
"the earth element."

msgctxt "sn14.32:1.3"
msgid ""
"Pathavīdhātuyāhaṃ, bhikkhave, ādīnavapariyesanaṃ acariṃ, yo pathavīdhātuyā "
"ādīnavo tadajjhagamaṃ, yāvatā pathavīdhātuyā ādīnavo paññāya me so sudiṭṭho."
msgstr ""
"I went in search of the earth element’s drawback, and I found it. I’ve seen "
"clearly with wisdom the full extent of the drawback in the earth element."

msgctxt "sn14.32:1.4"
msgid ""
"Pathavīdhātuyāhaṃ, bhikkhave, nissaraṇapariyesanaṃ acariṃ, yaṃ "
"pathavīdhātuyā nissaraṇaṃ tadajjhagamaṃ, yāvatā pathavīdhātuyā nissaraṇaṃ "
"paññāya me taṃ sudiṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
"I went in search of escape from the earth element, and I found it. I’ve seen "
"clearly with wisdom the full extent of escape from the earth element."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn14.32:2.1"
msgid "Āpodhātuyāhaṃ, bhikkhave … pe …"
msgstr "I went in search of the water element’s gratification …"

msgctxt "sn14.32:2.2"
msgid "tejodhātuyāhaṃ, bhikkhave …"
msgstr "I went in search of the fire element’s gratification …"

msgctxt "sn14.32:2.3"
msgid ""
"vāyodhātuyāhaṃ, bhikkhave, assādapariyesanaṃ acariṃ, yo vāyodhātuyā assādo "
"tadajjhagamaṃ, yāvatā vāyodhātuyā assādo paññāya me so sudiṭṭho."
msgstr "I went in search of the air element’s gratification …"

msgctxt "sn14.32:2.4"
msgid ""
"Vāyodhātuyāhaṃ, bhikkhave, ādīnavapariyesanaṃ acariṃ, yo vāyodhātuyā ādīnavo "
"tadajjhagamaṃ, yāvatā vāyodhātuyā ādīnavo paññāya me so sudiṭṭho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn14.32:2.5"
msgid ""
"Vāyodhātuyāhaṃ, bhikkhave, nissaraṇapariyesanaṃ acariṃ, yaṃ vāyodhātuyā "
"nissaraṇaṃ tadajjhagamaṃ, yāvatā vāyodhātuyā nissaraṇaṃ paññāya me taṃ "
"sudiṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.172"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn14.32:3.1"
msgid ""
"Yāvakīvañcāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imāsaṃ catunnaṃ dhātūnaṃ assādañca assādato "
"ādīnavañca ādīnavato nissaraṇañca nissaraṇato yathābhūtaṃ na abbhaññāsiṃ, "
"neva tāvāhaṃ, bhikkhave, sadevake loke samārake sabrahmake "
"sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiyā pajāya sadevamanussāya anuttaraṃ sammāsambodhiṃ "
"abhisambuddhoti paccaññāsiṃ."
msgstr ""
"As long as I didn’t truly understand these four elements’ gratification, "
"drawback, and escape for what they are, I didn’t announce my supreme perfect "
"awakening in this world with its gods, Māras, and Brahmās, this population "
"with its ascetics and brahmins, its gods and humans."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn14.32:4.1"
msgid ""
"Yato ca khvāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imāsaṃ catunnaṃ dhātūnaṃ assādañca assādato "
"ādīnavañca ādīnavato nissaraṇañca nissaraṇato yathābhūtaṃ abbhaññāsiṃ, "
"athāhaṃ, bhikkhave, sadevake loke samārake sabrahmake sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiyā "
"pajāya sadevamanussāya anuttaraṃ sammāsambodhiṃ abhisambuddhoti paccaññāsiṃ."
msgstr ""
"But when I did truly understand the four elements’ gratification, drawback, "
"and escape for what they are, I announced my supreme perfect awakening in "
"this world with its gods, Māras, and Brahmās, this population with its "
"ascetics and brahmins, its gods and humans."

msgctxt "sn14.32:4.2"
msgid "Ñāṇañca pana me dassanaṃ udapādi:"
msgstr "Knowledge and vision arose in me:"

msgctxt "sn14.32:4.3"
msgid "‘akuppā me vimutti, ayamantimā jāti, natthi dāni punabbhavo’”ti."
msgstr ""
"‘My freedom is unshakable; this is my last rebirth; now there are no more "
"future lives.’”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn14.32:4.4"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
